*arandr-0.1.8 (14 Jul 2015)

  14 Jul 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +arandr-0.1.8.ebuild:
  Version bump (bug #554228 by José Romildo Malaquias).

  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> arandr-0.1.7.1.ebuild:
  Drop old Python implementations

  08 Oct 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -arandr-0.1.6.ebuild:
  Old.

  08 Oct 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> arandr-0.1.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #486790

  05 Oct 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> arandr-0.1.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #486790

*arandr-0.1.7.1 (04 Mar 2013)

  04 Mar 2013; Julian Ospald <hasufell@gentoo.org> -arandr-0.1.7-r1.ebuild,
  +arandr-0.1.7.1.ebuild, -files/arandr-0.1.7-locale.patch:
  version bump wrt #460300, remove old

*arandr-0.1.7-r1 (03 Mar 2013)

  03 Mar 2013; Julian Ospald <hasufell@gentoo.org> -arandr-0.1.7.ebuild,
  +arandr-0.1.7-r1.ebuild, +files/arandr-0.1.7-locale.patch:
  fix locale behavior, add missing PYTHON_USEDEP to dependencies, remove
  unsupported python2_5, remove obsolete PYTHON_MODNAME variable, update
  license

  01 Mar 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> arandr-0.1.7.ebuild:
  Port to distutils-r1.

*arandr-0.1.7 (01 Mar 2013)

  01 Mar 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +arandr-0.1.7.ebuild:
  Version bump by chrysn (bug #459792). Add support for LINGUAS.

  21 Nov 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> arandr-0.1.6.ebuild:
